################# About Project ######################

In this project user can register himself/herself by signing up a form and after registration
user can login.

This project has the facility to reset the password when user will click on forgot password button next popup will appear where user have to write the email address to get the instruction or link to reset the password (Note reset link will come on the terminal or console)

Beyond that user can add or update the details of their own for ex -- name, city,locality and others.

And in the end user can logout himself/herself.

Also superuser can deactivate and activate the normal user as well.

This is brief description about the project.

In this project otp will not send on email it will come on the console because google has stopped the third party services less secure app access so smtp is not working .

################## End ###################################